sentence:
(RTTNews) - Below are the earnings highlights for Procter & Gamble Co. (PG):

-Earnings: -$5.24 billion in Q4 vs. $1.89 billion in the same period last year.
-EPS: -$2.12 in Q4 vs. $0.72 in the same period last year.
-Excluding items, Procter & Gamble Co. reported adjusted earnings of $2.90 billion or $1.10 per share for the period.
-Analysts projected $1.05 per share -Revenue: $17.09 billion in Q4 vs. $16.50 billion in the same period last year.
